first things first… In order to use Poly Studio, please consent to the conditions of the HP User License Agreement and Privacy Policy. I consent to the License Agreement Continue Up-to-Date Never miss an update. Use Poly Studio to update all your devices and ensure you always have the latest features. Personal Customize your settings and make your Poly devices work the way you want them to work. Let’s get started. Organized Can’t find your device? No problem. Poly Studio has a location feature to help you find a misplaced device. Enable location tracking now or later in Find My Device to stay current on your device’s location. Healthy Set reminders to hydrate and take screen breaks, or listen to relaxing sounds of nature while you work. Skip Enable now Log in to get the most out of your Poly Studio experience. Continue as Guest Clear Reset Are you sure you want to delete this device? License Agreement and Bluetooth off Turn on Bluetooth on your mobile device before using Poly Studio. Select Device Check back for future supported devices. New Feature unavailable. An internet connection is required to use this feature. None Settings Restored! Remember to unplug (if USB-connected) and power off/on your headset in order for your new settings to take effect. Device Product ID: Hardware Revision: You must update the software to access this feature.
