// DFU screen Start Update Software Update Let's Get Started! An update is available for your device. The update takes a few minutes to complete. Let's get started. Three Easy Steps Keep your device connected and next to the mobile device.

Don't close Poly Studio while updating.

Plug your phone into a power source. Updating Answering a call may interrupt the update and require you to restart the update once the call ends.

To avoid interruptions, we recommend completing the update before using your device for calls. Almost there, don't leave yet. Update Complete The software update for "%1$s" has successfully updated.

 Close this window to return to home screen. Houston… We have a problem.

The software update for "%1$s" didn't successfully complete.

Keep your Poly device and your mobile device nearby, connected to each other and the Internet. Your device battery doesn't have enough power to update the software.

Fully charge the device or plug it into a power source and try again. Device battery is too low to update the software. Connect your device to a power source and try again. Be sure your earbuds are out of the case, connected, and fully charged to complete the update. Device charging case battery is too low to update the software. Connect your device charging case to a power source and try again. Not enough battery remaining to update the software. Connect your device and charging case to a power source and try again. Device Settings can not be accessed during Software Update. Update currently not available, please try back later. Cannot update this device during a call. Software Update Complete Updating Software Verifying Updates Needed. Current: %1$s, Update Available: %2$s Update What type of issues do you have? Which device do you have issues with? Device App No previously connected devices were found. Please connect devices using the mobile device\’s Bluetooth Settings prior to requesting device support. Send the detailed information to Support.
Take a screen shot or write down the below
details for a faster process. App Version: Tenant Name: Tenant ID: User ID: App ID: Last Connected: Go Device Name: Serial Number: Product Support Help Guide Find My Device Make sure this device is being used as your main audio source to play tone. Sending tone… Near %1$s Unknown %1$s of %2$s Select Language Select the language you want for all voice prompts and alerts. For example, "Incoming call from John." or "Mute on." Select the language to use for all voice prompts and alerts. For example, "Incoming call from John." or "Mute on." No devices were found. Connect your Poly device using Bluetooth and try again. You must update the software to apply the selected language. The language change only applies to audio. Later Update Now Poly Privacy Policy About Licenses Third-party Software Source Share Data Don't Share Help us improve your experience. HP may collect basic device and app information, such as model, serial number, software version and feature usage, to help improve performance and support. This data doesn’t include any personal information and will not be shared with third parties. You can change your preferences at anytime in Settings. The app collects location data to enable Find My Device feature even when the app is closed or not in use. In order to use this feature you must give permission for location usage. In order to use this feature you must give permission for showing notifications. Your session has expired. You need to log in again. Enable now Cancel Turn on Location Services to allow "Poly Studio" to determine your location. Settings Cancel Something is wrong. Please check your network connection and try again. Warning! Exposure to high sound levels may cause permanent damage to your hearing.

 Make sure your device is not being worn by anyone before tapping “Play” to send a tone. Ok got it Please change your audio connection default to Media Audio to hear the tone. An update has just been downloaded. Restart Log in with your Poly Studio account to access useful information that can improve your support experience.
